**Challenge**: Desktop shows 3 opponents with full detail (name, tiles, melds). Mobile has limited space.

**Solution - Compact Opponent Cards**:

#### Desktop (Spacious)

```text
┌───────────────────────────┐
│ EAST: Alice               │
│ 👤 [Avatar]               │
│ Concealed: ████████████   │ (13 tiles shown)
│                           │
│ Exposed:                  │
│ Pung: 7D 7D 7D            │
└───────────────────────────┘

```

