**Challenge**: Desktop shows all 40+ discards in grid. Mobile can't fit.

**Solution - Bottom Sheet Modal**:

```text
User swipes up from center →

┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Discard Pile (24 tiles)  [×]    │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Recent (Last 6):                │
│ [5D] [3B] [JO] [2C] [9C] [1B]   │
