## 7. Typography & Readability

### 7.1 Minimum Font Sizes

**iOS Safari**: Automatically zooms text < 16px (annoying!).

**Solution**: Use 16px minimum for all body text.

```css
body {
  font-size: 16px; /* Prevents auto-zoom */
}

.tile-rank {
  font-size: 24px; /* Large, readable */
  font-weight: 700;
}

```

text

text

text

text

---

### 7.2 Line Height for Touch Targets

**Challenge**: Tappable links in paragraphs need space.

**Solution**: Increase line-height to 1.6 (desktop: 1.4).

```css
p {
  line-height: 1.6; /* 160% of font size */
}

a {
  padding: 8px 0; /* Vertical padding for touch */
  display: inline-block;
}

```

text

text

text

text

