## 8. Charleston on Mobile (Specific Challenge)

### 8.1 Selecting 3 Tiles from 13 on Small Screen

**Desktop**: Shift+Click range select (5 tiles selected in 2 clicks).

**Mobile**: No keyboard, no Shift key. Must tap 3 individual tiles.

**Problem**: 13 tiles × 48px = 624px wide. Screen is 375px. Horizontal scroll required.

**Solution - Tile Carousel with Selection Preview**:

```text
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Charleston: First Right Pass    │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Your Hand (swipe to scroll):    │
│                                 │
│ ← [1B][2B][3B][4B][5B] →        │ (5 visible, 8 hidden)
│                                 │
│ Selected (2/3):                 │
│ [4B] [5B] [   ]                 │ <- Preview area
│                                 │
│ [Confirm Pass ✓] (disabled)     │
└─────────────────────────────────┘

User swipes right, taps 9C:

┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Charleston: First Right Pass    │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Your Hand (swipe to scroll):    │
│                                 │
│ ← [7D][8D][9C][JO][E] →         │
│                                 │
│ Selected (3/3):                 │
│ [4B] [5B] [9C] ✅               │
│                                 │
│ [Confirm Pass ✓] (enabled)      │
└─────────────────────────────────┘

```

text

text

text

text

**Key UX Improvements**:

1. **Separate preview area**: Selected tiles shown in static area (no need to scroll back)

1. **Visual count**: "2/3" shows progress

1. **Confirm button state**: Disabled until 3 selected

1. **Scroll indicators**: Arrows show more tiles available

---

### 8.2 Blind Pass/Steal on Mobile

**Challenge**: On Last Left pass, players can "steal" 1-2 tiles from incoming pass.

**Desktop UX**: Select 1, 2, or 3 tiles. Button label changes: "Pass 1, Steal 2".

**Mobile Problem**: Button text too long for small screen: "Pass 1, Steal 2" → 16 characters.

**Solution - Icon-Based UI**:

```text
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Charleston: Last Left (Steal?)  │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Selected (1/3):                 │
│ [9C]                            │
│                                 │
│ Pass: 1 tile →                  │
│ Steal: 2 tiles ←                │
│                                 │
│ [Confirm ✓]                     │
└─────────────────────────────────┘

```

text

text

text

text

**Icons**:

- → (right arrow) = tiles you're passing

- ← (left arrow) = tiles you're stealing

